erver...</span><hr size=1> Just something I thought about the other day after reading about the new server.<br>
<br>
Wonder if this new rule set is some sort of new code for the game engine?  Aka wouldn't it be interesting if they made the new server accesable like test is.  Thru a different type of login server.  Also could this new server be set up for new testing of PvP in the game engine for their future games?  <br>
<br>
I myself hope that they do not allow slits from other servers to the new one.  The only reason I don't play on a PvP server is that I would play on Rallos for the full pvp action, but don't want to have to start at the bottom and work my way up thru everyone.  Now with this new server gives me a chance to start out like everyone else and not have any twinks to deal with,<br>
<br>
I do like the idea of the 1 thru 5 lvl non-pvp.  Actually lets those that want to play pvp able to get a fw lvls into the game before getting wasted by people comming over to kill others cause their normal server is down.  I also think it would rock if they limit the number of chars you can have on this server to 1 (one).  Less twinking this way.  <br>
<br>
Wouldn't it be nice if they make it open pvp aka no lvl limits on people you can attack.  Watch the high lvl guy come into the newbie area and get mobed by 40 newbies.  That would be interesting.  <br>
<br>
In reguards to the loot having it be 1 item and cash loot would be fair.  Only thing is with casters how much gear do they need?  They really don't need much armour for pvp do they?  I haven't played one so don't really know.<br>
<br>
Anyways back to my regular board brousing(sp?) {to early i the day for me still}.<br>
